  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add finely chopped garlic and chili peppers, cook for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Stir in finely diced onion and tomato, cook until softened and slightly browned.",
    "Fold in the dumplings gently with a spoon. Add salt to taste.",
    "Pour the lemon juice over everything, stirring quickly to combine all ingredients evenly.",
    "Serve hot as an accompaniment to rice or can be eaten on its own."
